{"tid":1165204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"葡萄牙Aptoide與華為洽談代替谷歌，侵侵明反華為暗滅谷歌？","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T16:01:34.000Z","uid":220850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a901b81229c48be702354d4fdab0431363db62d8","tid":1165204,"uid":220850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2143165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2143165&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=3fe7401f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2143165</a><br />\n<br />\n谷歌迫於美國政府&ldquo;禁令&rdquo;，宣布暫停支持華為的部分業務。路透社分析稱，此舉將導致華為智能手機無法使用谷歌應用商店Google Play等服務，華為在歐洲的手機業務可能受到衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n就在這時，一家葡萄牙第三方安卓應用商店站出來說：我們正在和華為談合作。<br />\n<br />\nAptoide在其內容商店為安卓(Android)作業系統提供了超過90萬個應用程式，擁有超過2億名活躍用戶。該公司已與中國智能手機製造商小米、OPPO和Vivo合作"},{"pid":"3be1924ece393dc297587b74240689fd1c9e7899","tid":1165204,"uid":249604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b0f08a980541bd456f5e6b3e43e291c61b0e6e7","tid":1165204,"uid":249604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:37:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97346312437e60ab7c1d66f1768b5267df8b5925","tid":1165204,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773de62483032a5e33d2c1c1c35393d1c8dbf380","tid":1165204,"uid":108245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"搞笑 肯定google 唔比錢佢搵"},{"pid":"474a553c1bd076b8c53fe5aab80a03361fe6befe","tid":1165204,"uid":254259,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}